  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and grated ginger to the pan, stirring for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Pour in chicken broth and white wine vinegar, bringing the mixture to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and stir in soy sauce and salt. Simmer for about 5 minutes or until thickened slightly.",
    "Fold in frozen dumplings gently using tongs. Let them cook for an additional 2-3 minutes or until fully heated through.",
    "Serve hot."
